Name: steamCLI
Version: 1.0.5
Summary: Find price information about games on Steam from the command line.
Home-page: https://github.com/vilisimo/steamCLI
Author: vilisimo
Author-email: vilisimo@gmail.com
License: MIT License
Description: The app provides a simple to use command line interface to check prices of  apps on Steam and compare them with historical lows. For that, https://isthereanydeal.com/ is used. To see a more in-depth and up-to-date description, please see the provided GitHub page.
